But this is an interesting one,

00:08:33.879 --> 00:08:36.048
because you technically failed
at the news division.

00:08:36.081 --> 00:08:37.783
You were demoted
to the talk show.

00:08:37.816 --> 00:08:39.184
-Yeah. -But the talk show
ended up being

00:08:39.217 --> 00:08:40.753
-the greatest promotion
